      "writtenOn": "2026-03-09T13:32:42Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "\u003e This seems like something we could just encapsulate entirely within the application?\n\nPossibly, but isn\u0027t this something for SPDM maintainers to look into as to how their design should be implemented?\n\nFunctionally it\u0027s just a D-Bus interface to probe on. Since we have the\n```\n        \"AND\",\n        \"FOUND(\u0027Huygens System Chassis\u0027)\"\n```\nit should not have any adverse effects on other systems, right?",
      "parentUuid": "65a9173c_17c0d133",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 13,
        "startChar": 0,
        "endLine": 13,
        "endChar": 132
      },
      "revId": "59e967528a781ca4e1dd19552294f88370e3a6db",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
    },
